entries.femaleVariant: [Cross bridge with Alt]
[Enter well and return to body]
"When the evening is spread out against the sky,"
"Let us go, through certain half-deserted streets,"
"The muttering retreats"
[Grab shoulder] You're here!
[Grab shoulder] I did it. Somehow, despite it all.
You're here!
I did it, Johnny. Despite it all, somehow, I did it.
You actually did it. You and that ragtag team of scrap-rats.
When do we start?
Time's short.
So, when do we start?
Did you see anything? Or were you completely cut out?
Were you with me the whole time?
Suppressors slowed me down, but yeah – I saw.
Lotta people died just for me to get here…
Sorry about Saul... It was my fault Smasher was here in the first place.
Should probably hurry before Arasaka sends reinforcements. Where's Alt?
"Like a patient etherized upon a table,"
"Let us go then, you and I,"
There's nothin' to talk about.
I-I can't believe it. Everything. A-all we did – it was pointless.
entries.maleVariant: I ca-- I can't believe it. Everything. All we did – it was pointless.

entries.femaleVariant: Wanna live out whatever life I got left.
I've had enough of this. Of everything. You most of all.
Perfect, 'cause we're stickin' to the plan. I'm goin' with Alt, fuck knows where, you're keepin' your body.
Body's Johnny's. I'll go.
Alt? What do I do?
Alt? If you were me, heh... what would you do?
What does that mean for me, exactly? Am I gonna... become like you?
entries.maleVariant: What's that mean for me, exactly? Am I gonna... become like you?

entries.femaleVariant: I was a netrunner. I understood how to survive. I cannot speak for you.
Yeah, we... stick to the plan. Johnny, I'm sorry.
entries.maleVariant: Yeah, we... we stick to the plan. Johnny, I'm sorry.

entries.femaleVariant: Johnny, change of plans. I go, you stay.
Don't apologize. We knew all along this's how it would play out.
Don't... don't fuck with me right now.
Only if you cut your pathetic “I’m sorry” bullshit.
I mean, Jesus, I'm about to shred a comrade and a chunk of my own soul in one fuckin' go. You have no idea what that shit feels like.
entries.maleVariant: I mean, Jesus, I'm about to shred a comrade and a chunk of my own soul in one fuckin' go. You got no idea what that shit feels like.

entries.femaleVariant: Hm. Sounds kinda familiar. We know that attitude... See, V? Stayin' with you whether you like it or not.
For fuck’s sake, defend yourself. You're not even trying!
Y’know, you taught me to let go sometimes, save my strength for one last big bang.
Goodbye, V. And never stop fightin’.
What, a little guilt creeps in and that's that? You give up?
Stop. Just stop.
Gonna just roll over instead of fightin' for what's yours, decomish yourself 'cause you're too fuckin' scared to say goodbye?
It is my decision, let me make it.
entries.maleVariant: It's my decision, let me make it.

entries.femaleVariant: You’re loyal, grant you that. But dammit are you dense. Haven't changed a bit since we met.
I’m so damn tired, Johnny. I just wanna start anew, even if I don't know what that means. I bet it'd be good for you, too.
V, I’m just... I’m just scared for ya...
I'll see ya 'round, Johnny.
Is this it? The infamous prison of souls?
Are we in Arasaka's prison of souls?
Not how I remember it, but Alt wasn't runnin' the show back then.
Fuck if I know. We only see what Alt wants us to see.
Devised a solid plan and pulled it off. That's you. Well done.
I'm sorry, not sure I quite caught that.
Then wash out your ears, you dumbass.
So where are all of Soulkiller's victims?
I can't believe this.
There's nothing to talk about.
Haven't caught on yet, have ya?
What-- Whaddaya mean?
entries.maleVariant: What? Whaddaya mean?

entries.femaleVariant: Alt's already split us. Once you jacked into Mikoshi, she lit you up with Soulkiller.
Hey, Alt.
Too bad. He coulda used someone like you.
You hit me with Soulkiller without asking?
Hey, Alt – so, seein' as we seem to have the soul splittin' outta the way, what's next?
Too bad. Johnny coulda used someone like you by his side.
You real? You hit me with Soulkiller?! 'Thout asking?!
Your output don't fuck around.
I am not his girlfriend.
It was the only way I could fulfill your request.
Jesus fuck, I'd've liked a warning at least…
Been a construct for just a few minutes and already no one gives a damn what you want. Welcome to the club, V.
Strong words from a fellow construct stuck in the same Arasaka prison.
Wait, what...? Mean to say I'm an engram?
Uh-huh, same as me. Got any more jokes?
I am currently verifying the checksum and eliminating engram copy errors in the process.
Wait, you mean... I... Am I a construct?
She means you followed in my footsteps. Next step's to copy you into the gonk's brain.
So, that's it. It's over.
Someone please explain.
Wait, hold on. I wanna know what the hell happened to me. Exactly!
I applied Soulkiller to separating your two psyches, thereby creating V's distinct construct. An added analgesic protocol precluded any perception of pain.
I was unable to eliminate all the changes made through the Johnny data incursion and overwrite, but V's engram integrity remains high.
Meaning, you can transfer her psyche back into her brain?
entries.maleVariant: Meaning, you can transfer his psyche back into his brain?

entries.femaleVariant: As if onto a blank, virgin partition.
So that's really it. We're done. You kept your word.
There is one aspect I failed to take into account.
Alt? What?
DNA reconfiguration by the Relic has progressed too far. Added to aggressive, invasive medications, the body's immune system attacking its own neurons…
Christ, will you just skip to the end?!
After I transfer your construct into your body, you will die. It is inevitable. It is imminent.
The body as a key factor in this transaction.
No. No, no way. That was not our deal.
entries.maleVariant: No. No way. That was not our deal.

entries.femaleVariant: No. No way.
You planned this. Both of you.
Shit...
Check again.
Had this planned all along, didn't you? Never had any intention of keepin' me alive.
entries.maleVariant: Had this planned all along, didn't ya? Never had any intention of keepin' me alive.

entries.femaleVariant: Are you absolutely sure? Check again.
Fuck…
You shall live for about six months. Perhaps somewhat more.
No, no, no...
There's gotta be somethin', somethin' we haven't thought of!
entries.maleVariant: There's gotta be somethin'... somethin' we haven't thought of!

entries.femaleVariant: Is that a fuckin' joke?
You backstabbing motherfucker. You just fuckin' kicked back, dumbass grin on your face, and waited till I finally realized you had me fucked from the start!
entries.maleVariant: You backstabbin' motherfucker! You just fuckin' kicked back, dumbass grin on your face, and you waited till I finally realized you had me fucked from the start.

entries.femaleVariant: Gonna pretend I didn't hear that.
Alt, question. Will the body reject Johnny's construct?
Alt, c'mon. There's gotta be a way outta this.
Your body will see you as an intruder.
But it's my body!
The biochip's nanites have altered it permanently. The body is now Johnny.
No. They are compatible. The body is his.
Alt, give us a minute. V and I need to talk.
That's enough, Alt. V and I need a minute.
Where's she even gonna take you?
Beyond the Blackwall, to become part of her. Whatever the hell that means.
We must have other options.
It's dangerous beyond the Blackwall.
What's it like, beyond the Blackwall?
Assuming I don't lose my fuckin' mind, at least no one can ride my ass there.
What about hangin' around as a construct? Just till we find another way?
Finding another way would mean makin' a deal with 'Saka. I'll pass.
Is there really no other way?
As I said, Johnny can retain the body, remain there, while you come with me.
Guess I meant, I dunno, a... a happier ending for everyone involved.
entries.maleVariant: Guess I meant, I dunno... a happier ending... for everyone involved.

entries.femaleVariant: Yet the right to make a choice you have earned, through will and endeavor.
Here, for folks like us? Wrong city, wrong people.
[Grab shoulder] Hey, V.
[Grab shoulder] Admit I was right. Told you I'd handle it.
Hey, V. Happy to see me?
Looks like I was right again. Told ya I'd handle it.
Rogue's gone.
Had to hack my way through a jungle.
Rogue's dead. Smasher was there.
You know 'Saka planted a fuckin' jungle on the top floors of its HQ? Had to hack my way through it with a machete to get here.
Shame you couldn't watch. It was my magnum opus. You'da loved it.
Hey, Alt? Where are you?
Alt? Gonna show yourself? Say "hi," maybe?
Soulkiller – we can't feel it doin' its thing. How come? Should be pissin' our panties in pain right now.
You'll be all right. I mean, look, you made it this far.
"Of restless nights in one-night cheap hotels"
"And sawdust restaurants and oyster-shells,"
"Streets that follow like a tedious argument"
"Of insidious intent"
"To lead you to an overwhelming question..."
"Oh, do not ask," 'What is it?'"
"Let us go and make our visit."
Good to see you too, Johnny.
You see any of what went down?
No, but that's probably for the best.
entries.maleVariant: Nope, but that's prolly for the best.

entries.femaleVariant: Not exactly. Blacked out, then woke up here. I miss anything?
I'm sorry...
Shouldn't be. Died for me, not for you.
Is my body still in one piece?
Parked it in Arasaka Tower's basement, plugged it into the network.
Missed my greatest performance.
Johnny, been waiting here I dunno how long and my nerves are frayed. Tell me if my body's in one piece.
entries.maleVariant: Johnny, been waitin' here I dunno how long and my nerves are frayed. Tell me if my body's in one piece.

entries.femaleVariant: Yeah, yeah, it's fine. Not counting some leeches and a few hundred mosquito bites.
Mean yours and Rogue's, don’t ya?
Rogue's dead.
Incidentally, you could stand to gain some muscle mass. Just sayin'.
I'm sorry.
Lemme add that to my to-do list for my next life. Right now, waitin' for your output to finish gutting my soul.
'Fraid things're pretty shit for me, too. Alt's hittin' me with Soulkiller, my nerves are in shreds.
entries.maleVariant: 'Fraid things're pretty fucked for me, too. Alt's hittin' me with Soulkiller, my nerves are in shreds.

entries.femaleVariant: Heh, figured as much. Your output's been torchin' my brain with Soulkiller for a good while now.
entries.maleVariant: Figured as much. Your output's been torchin' my brain with Soulkiller for a good while now.

entries.femaleVariant: You'll be all right.
So, we at the finish line? It's all in Alt's hands now?
I'm an engram now, a construct. Fuck.
Yeah, well, welcome to the club. Hey, Alt! You here?
Told me she's finishing the checksum, then she'll copy me back over into my flesh.
Awareness of what's happening right now – that just raunches.
Like, Alt neatly packed me into an engram. Couldn't even tell when... or how.
Guess Alt's gonna start moving this digital psyche I am back into my flesh, but... got no idea if I'll survive or what I'll be if I do.
So, this'd be... the end.
Soulkiller – why can't we feel it working?
Digital analgesia. We're data streams, certain sensation inputs can be blocked blah blah yadda yadda.
entries.maleVariant: Digital analgesia. We're data streams, certain sensations' inputs can be blocked blah blah blah yadda yadda.

entries.femaleVariant: Alt make ya suffer through an exhaustive lecture?
Imparted it instantly. Whatever. She did say she'd destroy Mikoshi... just as you agreed.
No.
I made a mistake in excluding the body as a factor.
What the-- Alt?
DNA reconfiguration has progressed too far. Added to aggressive, invasive medications, the body's immune system attacking its own neurons…
Spit it out! In human terms!
V will die independent of what I do. This is inevitable. This is imminent.
Alt! For fuck's sake!
For fuck's sake, Alt, you had one job and you fucked it up?!
Alt, there's gotta be a way.
This never had a chance to end well.
Check again.
Fuck...
This couldn't end well, we never stood a chance... dunno why we even fuckin' tried.
Check again! If V's engram is damaged, can't you fix her?
entries.maleVariant: Check again! If V's engram is damaged, can't you fix him?

entries.femaleVariant: Fuck...
I could not know the situation before conducting a thorough and precise diagnosis.
You promised this poor little shit a new life and you lied! You fuckin' lied!
Johnny, shut it for two seconds, will ya? Gotta think!
'Cause it's life, it's death, it's the struggle. The hell else we s'posed to fight for?
entries.maleVariant: Cause it's life, it's death, it's the struggle. The hell else we supposed to fight for?

entries.femaleVariant: Alt, check again. Parse it all. We gotta be sure.
You have approximately six months to live.
OK, OK, j-just shut the fuck up. I n-need to think!
Hardware – therein lies the problem. The organism's neurons have been dying for a time. Any attempt at a procedure upon its brain would result in the latter's death.
You're a fucking genius! Think of something!
Enough, Johnny! Shut up! I need to think!
Couldn'ta said it better myself.
What the hell? What now?
Lemme... lemme think.
entries.maleVariant: OK, lemme... lemme think.

entries.femaleVariant: V, we'll think of a way.
Gonna be all right, V. We'll think of somethin'.
The biochip has irreversibly changed the host organism. It no longer belongs to V, who is an intruder there.
The situation is different for you. All changes were made to accomodate you.
Hang on, tellin' your ex to kick me outta my own body?
I said, gimme one fuckin' minute!
The changes are irreversible. You have nothing left to lose, he has everything to gain.
Give us a sec, Alt.
V, not doing that to you, no way.
Gotta admit, sounds reasonable, what Alt's saying.
Alt, give us a minute.
Got zero intentions of doin' you wrong. We made a deal, I'm stickin' to it.
Y'know, Alt might have a point. Your luck's run out, mine hasn't just yet.
You're my friend, V. I'd never pull that on you, never do you wrong.
I'd hope so.
Know what? I couldn't give a pig's prick what you think.
What the hell for, so you can trick me into agreeing? Giving you a free pass, even though you can already do what you want with my body?
entries.maleVariant: What the hell for, so you can trick me into agreeing? Givin' you a free pass, even though you can already do what you want with my body?

entries.femaleVariant: Are you fucking kidding me?
Never. You're my friend.
Let's think about what to do.
Let's talk this out calmly.
I don't give a shit what you think.
I just wanna discuss our options. Calmly.
There are no options, you two-faced sack of shit! You're out, I'm in – that was the deal!
Actually – know what? No!
Let's just think a sec... about what to do.
Right, OK. If that's what you want...
I stay. You fuck off. That's the deal.
Never thought I'd actually come to like you, but I have. I really do now.
Listen, Johnny... I'm glad we met, got to know each other. And I'm sorry.
If I only could, I'd turn back time. To that moment I got my hands on the fucking chip.
entries.maleVariant: If I only could, I'd turn back time. To that moment I got my hands on the fuckin' chip.

entries.femaleVariant: I will not interfere in your personal affairs, but while Johnny has full control, he can do what he wishes.
I don't wanna die. Who does? But I just don't see a way out...
Johnny... I'm sorry.
Enough. Could honestly talk in circles till the goddamn sun implodes.
OK, easy... Think too big a dose of Silverhand wound up in my blood. Need to chill.
But I told you once already and haven't changed my mind.
Still got a life to live, so you should go...
Listen, if I had to choose who to hole up with on a desert island, it wouldn't be you. Ever. Hell, the whole cast of "Little Big Corporats" would have you beat.
'Cause you're a dickhead, in a big way. And sure, plenty of others out there are more deserving of life. But even so... I'd never wish you dead.
entries.maleVariant: 'Cause you're a dickhead, in a big way. And sure, plenty of others out there're more deservin' of life. But even so... I'd never wish you dead.

entries.femaleVariant: Seeing as how I'm doomed to die, we stick to the plan I gave you – I leave, you stay. Keys to my body are yours.
entries.maleVariant: Seein' as how I'm doomed to die, we stick to the plan I gave you – I leave, you stay. Keys to my body are yours.

entries.femaleVariant: Goin' with Alt, you live on.
Goin' with Alt, you live on.
I wanna live.
Not ready to die yet.
No... It's gonna be me.
OK, yeah... Can't say I wasn't hoping you would say that.
So, what do I do, Alt?
Simply cross the bridge.
Johnny...
Don't make this any harder, eh? Just... don't forget I came 'round.
What do I do, Alt?
Simply enter the well.
If you're not ready to die, then... you're gonna live.
Yeah, I... wouldn't mind hangin' around a while longer.
You should come with me.
Beyond the Blackwall dangers lurk, it is no sanctuary. But it's better to be a free spirit shredded than to wither, trapped in a dying body.
Who was right, you cranky bastard?
Hah. You were right, V. You were.
Hohoh… And who just ate their words?
entries.maleVariant: Heheh… And who just ate their words?

entries.femaleVariant: Oh, fuck off.
[Grab shoulder] I did it! It's all come together!
[Grab shoulder] Ready to get outta my head?
It worked! I'm gonna fuckin' live!
Hey, Johnny.
All packed, you washout? Got your one-way ticket?
This funny to you?
Y'know, discovered one nice thing about becomin' Johnny Silverhand. You stop givin' the slimmest shit about Johnny Silverhand.
That right? This mean you've already decided what comes next?
Gotta admit, you cobbled together a good plan.
Been my curse and my nightmare, Johnny, but I do owe you one thing.
I'm kickin' your ass out.
Want a word with Alt first.
Johnny, not gonna lie. But you'd best prepare your ass for the fuckin' kick of the century.
Want a word with Alt first. Where is the wench?
Day to day, with Silverhand by my side, I learned to kick down barriers. Now, nothin' can hold me back. I can feel it.
Got no idea where you'll land after it, but sure hope it'll be far away from me.
Is that so? Meanin' you've made a decision about us?
Alt? Alt! You here?
You two still plan to obliterate Mikoshi?
Still plan to destroy Mikoshi?
Mhm. It's gotta burn.
What about everyone locked away there?
I will free them, take them with me.
Cut the crap. You'll gobble 'em up like so many morsels of code, make 'em part of you.
As if they could hope for anything better. C'mon...
But I do... even though it's simple. Not ready to die yet, Johnny, I wanna live. Exactly nothing's changed since that time we talked at the Pistis Sophia.
Don't need to explain, V.
We'll find a way.
No, Johnny, we won't. We're outta options. And I don't have the strength to keep fighting.
entries.maleVariant: No, Johnny, we won't. We're out of options. And I don't have the strength to keep fighting.

entries.femaleVariant: Remember what I told you? When we talked at the Pistis Sophia.
Yeah. Said you'd take a bullet for me.
Uh-huh. And I haven't changed my mind. But this bullet's aimed my way, so I just gotta make sure I don't drag you down into the grave with me.
entries.maleVariant: Yeah. And I haven't changed my mind. But this bullet's aimed my way, so I just gotta make sure I don't drag you down into the grave with me.

entries.femaleVariant: Just promise me one thing, asshole.
You won't forget me.
Gonna release all those poor bastards only to suck them into her own bosom, make them part of herself.
I told you... I said I wanted you to have my body.
What I told you at the Pistis Sophia – we stick to that.
But... but I can't do it... I'm sorry.
I'll go. You stay.
So whaddaya think? Like bein' a clump of ones and zeros?
At first, the phantom pain... Jesus. Felt like my whole body was on fire. Realize now it's not pain at all, just some digital simulacrum.
entries.maleVariant: At first, the phantom pain... Jesus. Felt like my whole body was on fire. Realize now it's not pain at all, it's just some digital simulacrum.

entries.femaleVariant: Didn't think life was worth clinging to. Not at any price, anyway.
Death is better than some digital afterlife.
That light gives me hope.
Jesus, to be a shapeless shadow in a digital afterlife... Really think I'd rather die.
It is freedom from the body's limitations, from the base worries of life in the world. It is a new perspective on all.
No, be left with fading memories... of sharing a bed, headsplitting hangovers, sea breeze on my face, sun's heat on my shoulders... No.
'Cause it ain't.
Wrong. That light beyond the Blackwall, see? That's hope.
Could be the flames of hell or heaven's grace. Might also be an engram reading code. But it's a promise of survival.
We've learned how to turn into pure data, but an animal still prowls inside us. And its instinct to survive almost can't be extinguished.
So take back your life – the six months you got left.
Yeah, that instinct's part of being human – but so is denying it.
Don't do it, V. You been runnin' from this all along. It'll change you. You won't be you anymore.
And you?
Already took that first step a while back. I'll have an easier go of it.
"Once out of nature I shall never take"
"My bodily form from any natural thing,"
"But such a form as Grecian goldsmiths make"
"Of hammered gold and gold enamelling"
"To keep a drowsy Emperor awake;"
"Or set upon a golden bough to sing"
"To lords and ladies of Byzantium"
"Of what is past, or passing, or to come."
Wanna live out whatever life I got left.
Body's Johnny's. I'll go.
This bridge leads deeper into cyberspace. Cross it and permanently sever the connection with your body.
The path to your body passes through that mortal well.
Got no idea what I feel.
Not gonna mount a defense?
Leave me alone.
It's my damned decision.
Just fuckin' tired.
G'bye, Johnny.
Don't forget me.
Don't forget me.
Don't forget me.
[Sit]
No need to explain.
No need to explain.
[Get up]
[Enter well and return to body]
[Punch Johnny]
V's life will be restored as it was before. You will become part of something greater.
You will become a part of me as V's body and former life are restored.
You will be reborn in V's body while V becomes a part of me.
V's body will be yours, while V will become a part of me.
Johnny, my friend…
Johnny...
You lied to me, from the start…
You lying sack of shit…
Got nothing to go back to, Johnny. Not so for you.
Alt, take me, goin' with you.
Normal again, Johnny – that's what I wanna be.
Wanna live out whatever time I got left.
As a netrunner, you will find your way through a materially limitless world.
Remember me.
Don't forget me.
I won't… ever.
Goodbye, V.
